take mind in a direction. If =\r\nyou mind has and exerts shakti, the enemies are stopped (fully or partially=\r\n) and the their push on the mind is negated.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;When you eat, you get p=\r\nhysical energy.\n When you exercise, that physical energy is stored in the r=\r\night places of the body. Similarly, when your mind spends time in a state o=\r\nf focused calmness, it eats from the universal source of shakti and gets no=\r\nurished. When it spends time in patterns of regulated exercises (e.g. homam=\r\n, japam, bhajan, satsang etc), it stores that shakti in the right places in=\r\n the mind.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Just as physical energy helps you fight external enemies =\r\nwho attack you, this spiritual energy helps you fight internal enemies who =\r\nattack you.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;If your surrender is perfect and you are going through t=\r\nhe good and bad fruits of your karmas without committing new karmas, your p=\r\noint is right. You are like a weightless leaf and you need no energy - you =\r\ngo with the flow. But, if you still have a conditioned mind that is vulnera=\r\nble to attacks from shadripus and vulnerable to committing NEW karmas, don&#39;=\r\nt you think some energy is needed?&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Don&#39;t look at spiritual shakti as=\r\n\n something that enables you to do great deeds in the world. Though that to=\r\no is possible, that is a ego-promiting attitude and inappropriate for most =\r\nsadhakas. Looks at spiritual shakti as something that enables you to fight =\r\nback your own internal enemies and overcome your own weaknesses.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;* *=\r\n *&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;4. If you are living every second without any goals/agendas/ wish=\r\nes/anticipat ions at all, then you are all already liberated and then your =\r\npoint is meaningful.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;But, if you do have some some goals, some wishe=\r\ns, some anticipations, some agendas etc, then you should realize that those=\r\n wishes and anticipations have a kinetic energy of their own (kaarmically) =\r\nand they bind you further. You need the spiritual energy (shakti) accumulat=\r\ned through exertion of self-control to negate that kinetic energy and stop =\r\nyou from getting bound further.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Some people make the mistake of thin=\r\nking that desire of moksha is also a desire and can stop you from\n moksha. =\r\nThat is true. However, it is better than many other desires and definitely =\r\nworth having. It can be jettisoned when the time comes.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Suppose you =\r\nhave a trash can in which you collect trash. Just throw away the collected =\r\ntrash and hang on to the trash can. If you throw away the can too, then new=\r\n trash that comes in will be all over the floor. So keep the can so that yo=\r\nu keep collecting trash and throwing it away. You can throw away the trash =\r\ncan also, when you are absolutely sure that no trash is being generated.&lt;BR=\r\n&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Best regards,&lt;BR&gt;Narasimha&lt;BR&gt;------------ --------- --------- -------=\r\n-- --------- --------- -&lt;BR&gt;Free Jyotish Software, Free Jyotish Lessons, Jy=\r\notish Writings,&lt;BR&gt;&quot;Do It Yourself&quot; ritual manuals for short Homam and Pitr=\r\ni Tarpana:&lt;BR&gt;&lt;A href=3D&quot;http://www.vedicastrologer.org/&quot; target=3D_blank r=\r\nel=3Dnofollow&gt;http://www.VedicAst rologer.org&lt;/A&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Films that make a diff=\r\nerence: &lt;A href=3D&quot;http://saraswatifilms.org/&quot; target=3D_blank\n rel=3Dnofol=\r\nlow&gt;http://SaraswatiFil ms.org&lt;/A&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Spirituality: &lt;A href=3D&quot;http://group=\r\ns.yahoo.com/group/vedic-wisdom&quot; target=3D_blank rel=3Dnofollow&gt;http://group=\r\ns. yahoo.com/ group/vedic- wisdom&lt;/A&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Jyotish writings: &lt;A href=3D&quot;http:=\r\n//groups.yahoo.com/group/JyotishWritings&quot; target=3D_blank rel=3Dnofollow&gt;ht=\r\ntp://groups. yahoo.com/ group/JyotishWri tings&lt;/A&gt;&lt;BR&gt;------------ --------=\r\n- 